11 (b) Notwithstanding any general or special law to the contrary, an agency that is a
12 member of the state retirement system pursuant to chapter 32 shall be deemed to be or shall
13 continue to be a member of the state retirement system.
14 (c) An agency shall not be required to annually reimburse the state board of retirement
15 for its pro rata share of any retirement allowance or pension paid by said board during the
